com.obdobion.excom.ui.module

Class Empty

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.obdobion.excom.ui.module.Empty
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPluginCommand

    public class Empty
extends Object
implements IPluginCommand

    Menu class.

    This is a placeholder class in that it does nothing in the execute method. Its purpose is to stop the interactive session. The InteractiveConsole looks for the name of this command to stop. But by having this IPluginCommand it will appear in the menu.
    Author:
    Chris DeGreef fedupforone@gmail.com
